{"tid":1684724,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"漢人聚新疆女，可獲7萬元及30萬呎田地","createTime":"2019-10-31T08:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T14:21:27.000Z","uid":149978,"like":11,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"3ad09ca7cb63340f607d92d2a45942f9af77b26b","tid":1684724,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:46:27.000Z","msg":"新疆擴大漢化政策<br />\n漢人娶疆女可得50畝田（約30萬呎田地）及7萬元現金<br />\n<br />\n【新唐人北京時間2019年10月30日訊】中共當局正在擴大推行在新疆的漢化政策，日前，網路熱傳，大陸漢族人到新疆落戶，新疆阿拉爾市政府會為其提供50畝包產地及建房補貼等獎勵，娶新疆女，會再得50畝機動地以及7萬元現金，引發外界關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/10/30/a102696368.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F10%2F30%2Fa102696368.html&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=d07f5c17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/10/30/a102696368.html</a>"},{"pid":"fbc477fa56b1e23d6ee9b8e54d7b64199d959de4","tid":1684724,"uid":282490,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"新疆女唔撚想嫁呢啲人渣喎"},{"pid":"4573e048c72495e9c25f3753e9d643b6775cefee","tid":1684724,"uid":65912,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"fbc477fa56b1e23d6ee9b8e54d7b64199d959de4","tid":1684724,"uid":282490,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"新疆女唔撚想嫁呢啲人渣喎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:58:50.000Z","msg":"可能被逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef044b7d29e420a9df5285b6e4c6e1bad7f69dee","tid":1684724,"uid":149978,"like":6,"dislike":21,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"fbc477fa56b1e23d6ee9b8e54d7b64199d959de4","tid":1684724,"uid":282490,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"新疆女唔撚想嫁呢啲人渣喎"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"有錢有地，點會唔想嫁？<br />\n唔通嫁俾新疆窮撚咩大？<br />\n有錢駛得鬼推磨呀。<br />\n仲有你娶新疆男，要入集中營和再教育營<br />\n娶漢人，有錢又有地<br />\n<br />\n俾你係新疆女，你會嫁俾邊個？"},{"pid":"b418